The box model
 - All elements are

 content box
 padding
 border
 margin

css:
  <style type="text/css">CSS-CODE</style>
 html:
  <link rel="stleshheet" href="the-css-file-css">

theSelector:first-child
the-selector:focus
theSelector:hover
theSelector:visited

css units
  Absolute:
    - Ccm, mm, in, px, pt...
    - Usually does not work well on different screen sizes
  Relative:
   - % - percentage of parent
   - em
   - vw - percentage of View Width
   - vh % of view height
   - vmin
   - vmax




Undvik globala variabler - använd variabler i funktioner istället
Strict mode - "use strict" för att aktivera
